RESTFUL ROUTES

name    url         verb    desc
INDEX   /dogs       GET     Display alist of all dog
NEW     /dogs/new   GET     Disply form to make a new dog
CREATE  /dogs       POST    Add new dog to DB
show    /dogs/:id    GET    Show info about one dog 



